      </section>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="methodology-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our AI Analysis Methodology</h2>
      <p>
        Our AI processes thousands of Amazon customer reviews using advanced natural language processing (NLP). 
        We extract sentiment on key attributes like efficacy, texture, absorption, value, and long-term results. 
        Products are scored based on verified purchase reviews, weighted by recency and reviewer credibility. 
        Only products with 1,500+ reviews qualify for top spots.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="disclaimer-section">
